{"article_id":"JiCrh6bjuTKeQ2p4","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Roger Stone has long feared","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"he would be slapped with a gag order","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"if he got indicted","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"- and he ' s readied a plan","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"to make sure","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"he won ' t have to stay silent .","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"The federal judge in Stone ' s case , Amy Berman Jackson , has already hushed a coterie of others","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"caught in special counsel Robert Mueller ' s dragnet ,","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"including Paul Manafort , Rick Gates and their attorneys .","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"They were quieted","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"after one of the lawyers told reporters","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"that Mueller ' s case was \" ridiculous . \"","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"Jackson will have a much longer record of public commentary from Stone","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"to work with","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"when the longtime Donald Trump associate appears Friday afternoon for his first status hearing","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"tied to the special counsel ' s charges","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"that he lied to Congress","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"and obstructed the House investigation into Russian election meddling .","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"If Stone is gagged ,","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"his contingency plan is already in place .","depth":5},{"id":20,"text":"He ' s got a well-known First Amendment attorney on his legal team","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"who represented the rap group 2 Live Crew against obscenity charges in the early 1990s .","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"And Stone has designated a pair of close friends as spokesmen in the event","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"he and his lawyers are told to stop talking .","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"Since his arrest last Friday , Stone has been on a media blitz .","depth":4},{"id":25,"text":"He gave his first interview to the conspiracy theory website InfoWars","depth":5},{"id":26,"text":"and then addressed reporters outside the federal courthouse in Fort Lauderdale .","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"He ' s discussed his legal defense plans during a series of interviews with the major television and cable networks , as well as in impromptu press conferences outside his South Florida home .","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"Anyone on Stone ' s email list got a message Monday with the subject line","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"\" Let ' s talk about my arrest \"","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"and a plea for \" emergency \" contributions","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"to help pay his mounting legal bills .","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"On Instagram , Stone as of Tuesday night had posted 30 times about the indictment ,","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"including a mock-up photograph of the special counsel in a waiter outfit","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"holding up a tray","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"topped with an empty hamburger bun .","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"\" Here ' s what Mueller has on me","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"# nothingburger \"","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"Stone wrote .","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"\" It ' s always been Roger ' s intention to maintain his First Amendment rights throughout the process , \"","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"said Michael Caputo , a longtime Stone associate and one of the people","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"who is in position","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"to step up as a spokesman","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"if Stone gets gagged .","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"During Stone ' s arraignment hearing on Tuesday , magistrate judge Deborah Robinson opened with a warning","depth":5},{"id":45,"text":"that he ' d be wise to not speak about the charges in the indictment .","depth":5},{"id":46,"text":"\" Any statements","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"you make","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"may be used against you , \"","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"she said .","depth":5},{"id":50,"text":"But Grant Smith , one of Stone ' s attorneys , said in an interview","depth":4},{"id":51,"text":"that Robinson ' s comments appeared to him to be pro forma .","depth":4},{"id":52,"text":"And on social media , Stone acted","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"as though he is still free to speak out .","depth":6},{"id":54,"text":"\" No gag order !","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"I will fight","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"and the deep state is in panic mode !","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"Onward , \"","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"Stone wrote Tuesday afternoon in an Instagram post","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"that featured a picture of him","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"surrounded by police officers outside the Washington , D.C. , federal courthouse .","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"Tuesday night , Stone appeared on Fox News with host Laura Ingraham","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"- his third interview on the conservative cable network since his arrest .","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"Appearing Monday night with Sean Hannity ,","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"Stone argued","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"that Mueller had charged him for \" errors of memory \"","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"and later played the gag order card .","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"\" They want to silence me","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"because I stand up for Donald Trump , \"","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"\" That ' s what this is really about . \"","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"Come Friday , many legal experts expect","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"that Stone will be in for a rude awakening with Jackson , a no-nonsense judge","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"appointed by President Barack Obama","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"who reacts harshly to what she perceives as showboating .","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"From the very beginning of the Manafort case in the fall of 2017 , she chafed at statements","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"his defense lawyer made ,","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"both inside and outside courtroom .","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"\" This is a criminal trial ,","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"and it ' s not a public relations campaign , \"","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"the judge warned at the first hearing","depth":13},{"id":81,"text":"she held in the Manafort case ,","depth":13},{"id":82,"text":"a little more than a week after his late October 2017 indictment .","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"\" I expect counsel to do their talking in this courtroom and in their pleadings and not on the courthouse steps . \"","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"Jackson immediately floated the idea of a gag order under a court rule","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"that permits them in \" widely publicized or sensational criminal cases. \"","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"Neither side objected ,","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"so less than a week later she fired off such an order .","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"On its face , the edict","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"Jackson issued in the Manafort case","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"didn ' t ban all public statements by the lawyers involved ,","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"but she made clear","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"as the case progressed","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"that she viewed it as barring any out-of-court remarks","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"that could influence how a jury would view the case .","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"Such gag orders are often more of a burden on the defense than the prosecution ,","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"since prosecutors typically issue a news release or hold a news conference","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"to announce the charges","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"and then go mum about the case - at least officially .","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"In addition , Justice Department policies discourage government attorneys from the kinds of statements","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"most gag orders would rule out .","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"Following the rules didn ' t turn out to be easy for Manafort ,","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"who has since pleaded guilty to one set of Mueller ' s charges","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"and been convicted in a separate case on bank and tax fraud charges .","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"Within a matter of months of his initial indictment , he found himself in hot water over the gag order","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"after prosecutors used intercepted emails","depth":13},{"id":106,"text":"to accuse him of secretly trying to orchestrate an op-ed in a Ukraine newspaper .","depth":13},{"id":107,"text":"Manafort ' s lawyers said","depth":12},{"id":108,"text":"it wasn ' t clear the order applied to him or to something","depth":13},{"id":109,"text":"to be published thousands of miles away .","depth":13},{"id":110,"text":"Jackson let Manafort off the hook that time with a mild rebuke .","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"But she was less forgiving","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"after Manafort was accused of witness tampering last spring ,","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"and the judge cited his earlier actions","depth":14},{"id":114,"text":"related to the gag order","depth":14},{"id":115,"text":"as contributing to her decision","depth":14},{"id":116,"text":"to order him jailed","depth":15},{"id":117,"text":"pending trial .","depth":15},{"id":118,"text":"\" This is not the first time","depth":12},{"id":119,"text":"we ' ve had to talk about the rules , and about you skating close to the line , \"","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"she told him in June 2018 .","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"Manafort ' s lawyers said on several occasions","depth":7},{"id":122,"text":"that they planned to file a pleading with the court","depth":8},{"id":123,"text":"arguing for a narrower interpretation of the gag order .","depth":8},{"id":124,"text":"They never did .","depth":6},{"id":125,"text":"Stone ' s associates say","depth":8},{"id":126,"text":"he ' ll contest any judicial moves","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"to shut him up .","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"\" If they put a gag order on him","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"I ' m quite certain","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"he ' ll fight it , \"","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"Caputo said .","depth":8},{"id":132,"text":"Shanlon Wu , a former attorney for Gates , said","depth":9},{"id":133,"text":"Stone could make the move","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"and perhaps narrow the order ,","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"and it also could help win a pardon from Trump .","depth":10},{"id":136,"text":"But Wu warned","depth":10},{"id":137,"text":"it could also tick off the judge .","depth":10},{"id":138,"text":"\" Most criminal defense lawyers don ' t want to antagonize the judge about something collateral , \"","depth":10},{"id":139,"text":"Wu said .","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"In Stone ' s case , Wu said","depth":9},{"id":141,"text":"a fight over his First Amendment rights might be a wasted effort .","depth":9},{"id":142,"text":"\" It ' s not an obscenity trial .","depth":11},{"id":143,"text":"It ' s not that he was arrested","depth":12},{"id":144,"text":"for protesting , ''","depth":12},{"id":145,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":146,"text":"\" Nine out of 10 lawyers would say ,","depth":10},{"id":147,"text":"' Hey , just shut up","depth":11},{"id":148,"text":"and let us do our job","depth":12},{"id":149,"text":"and don ' t make things worse . ' \"","depth":12},{"id":150,"text":"If Stone chooses the combative route","depth":9},{"id":151,"text":"when facing a gag order ,","depth":9},{"id":152,"text":"the dispute could end up before the D.C . Circuit Court of Appeals .","depth":8},{"id":153,"text":"An appeals court fight over a gag order is uncommon , but not unheard of , in federal criminal cases in Washington .","depth":8},{"id":154,"text":"Such a dispute erupted last year","depth":11},{"id":155,"text":"when lawyers for James Wolfe , a Senate Intelligence Committee staffer","depth":14},{"id":156,"text":"accused of lying to the FBI during a leak investigation ,","depth":14},{"id":157,"text":"tried to expand a gag order","depth":14},{"id":158,"text":"to cover the president .","depth":14},{"id":159,"text":"The request came","depth":13},{"id":160,"text":"after Trump publicly disparaged Wolfe after his arrest .","depth":13},{"id":161,"text":"The judge ultimately declined to issue an order","depth":11},{"id":162,"text":"that would reach the president .","depth":11},{"id":163,"text":"Indeed , legal experts noted","depth":10},{"id":164,"text":"that no Mueller-related gag order can blunt the intense media coverage , cable news chatter and steady flow of Trump tweets .","depth":10},{"id":165,"text":"Annemarie McAvoy , another former member of the Gates defense team , predicted","depth":9},{"id":166,"text":"a silencing dictate will probably come soon from Jackson against Stone .","depth":9},{"id":167,"text":"\" It is unlikely any judge is going to want a defendant in the public eye","depth":11},{"id":168,"text":"commenting about a case to the extent","depth":12},{"id":169,"text":"that Roger Stone has been doing , \"","depth":12},{"id":170,"text":"she said ,","depth":10},{"id":171,"text":"adding","depth":11},{"id":172,"text":"that Stone would face the harsh backstop of a criminal contempt order","depth":13},{"id":173,"text":"- punishable with fines and jail -","depth":13},{"id":174,"text":"if he doesn ' t comply .","depth":12},{"id":175,"text":"\" He will abide by it ,","depth":12},{"id":176,"text":"because he will understand","depth":13},{"id":177,"text":"that he will otherwise be subject to significant negative ramifications from the court , \"","depth":13},{"id":178,"text":"McAvoy said .","depth":11},{"id":179,"text":"For his part , Manafort has been in jail since last June ,","depth":10},{"id":180,"text":"and his lawyers have said in legal briefs","depth":10},{"id":181,"text":"that his time in solitary confinement has contributed to deteriorating mental and physical health ,","depth":10},{"id":182,"text":"including a case of gout","depth":11},{"id":183,"text":"that landed him in a wheelchair for several months .","depth":11},{"id":184,"text":"That ' s the chilling reality","depth":10},{"id":185,"text":"facing Stone ,","depth":11},{"id":186,"text":"who told in an interview last May","depth":12},{"id":187,"text":"that his plan was to keep talking","depth":14},{"id":188,"text":"until Mueller files any charges","depth":14},{"id":189,"text":"- and then to keep on talking afterward .","depth":13},{"id":190,"text":"\" The most dangerous thing is to go silent , \"","depth":11},{"id":191,"text":"Stone said then .","depth":11},{"id":192,"text":"\" When you ' re silent ,","depth":11},{"id":193,"text":"people assume","depth":12},{"id":194,"text":"you ' re guilty of something . \"","depth":12}],"relations":[{"parent":389,"left":238,"right":388,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":238,"left":218,"right":237,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":218,"left":212,"right":217,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":212,"left":200,"right":211,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":200,"left":197,"right":199,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":197,"left":196,"right":2,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":196,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":199,"left":3,"right":198,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":198,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":211,"left":205,"right":210,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":205,"left":202,"right":204,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":202,"left":201,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":201,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":204,"left":9,"right":203,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":203,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":210,"left":206,"right":209,"relation":"context","nuclearity":